article.headline: Stephen F. Austin 85, Texas College 52
article.story: NACOGDOCHES, Texas (AP) -- Antuane Miller scored 19 points and Josh Alexander had 15 as Stephen F. Austin beat Texas College 85-52 on Tuesday night. Mike Dale led Texas College (1-1) with 18 points. Miller was 7-of-9 off the bench in just 18 minutes for the Lumberjacks (3-3), who never trailed and shot 57 percent from the field. Matt Kingsley and Chaz Dykes each added 10 points for Sam Houston State. Antoine Ruelas had 14 points for Texas College and Jameus Hartsfield added six points and 10 rebounds.
